{"tid":936670,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"MSCI指數投資認真討論區","createTime":"2018-12-11T03:02:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T16:23:53.000Z","uid":57424,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e3cb6876b6b48dc2a1670bede74f1b0b133ed72d","tid":936670,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T03:02:18.000Z","msg":"What is MSCI?:<br />\n<del>MSCI公司（原Morgan Stanley Capital International和MSCI Barra）是一家美國股票基金、收入型基金、對沖基金股價指數和股東權益投資組合分析工具提供商。它發佈MSCI BRIC、MSCI World和MSCI EAFE指數。</del><br />\n簡單D黎講, 提供一個指數去投資一個市場, 而代表果個市場既成份股會比較本地比較真係代表倒當地經濟, 例如 2800 入面有騰訊 700, 而 MSCI Hong Kong 係冇!<br />\n<br />\n點解要跟 MSCI 去投資?:<br />\n因為可以極方便通過 ETF 既方便投資主世界, 依只係彈指之間完成, 唔洗專業人士幫你買賣!<br />\n<br />\n點解要投資全世界唔只係投資香港同強國?<br />\n因為個世界真係好大, 其他場市升副除時仲高, 你可以會搵倒下一個強國<br />\n<br />\nMSCI 有邊D ETF 可以擇?<br />\n呢到基本上有哂全球既市場<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ishares.com/us/literature/brochure/access-the-globe-with-ishares-etfs-en-us.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ishares.com%2Fus%2Fliterature%2Fbrochure%2Faccess-the-globe-with-ishares-etfs-en-us.pdf&d=nP9n0xxTvs6c74aFzLq0LACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=8522eb01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ishares.com/us/literature/brochure/access-the-globe-with-ishares-etfs-en-us.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n歡迎咁多位放眼世界既巴打一齊討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48f596c62a2c538c2c424c692a183afee8f4eaf5","tid":936670,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T03:08:32.000Z","msg":"想問吓投資呢啲扣唔扣股息稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b29abe4cf88c09bad76e25b16889bab5d9f2d6a6","tid":936670,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48f596c62a2c538c2c424c692a183afee8f4eaf5","tid":936670,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T03:08:32.000Z","msg":"想問吓投資呢啲扣唔扣股息稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},